416
00:26:50.436 --> 00:26:51.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:26:51.636 --> 00:26:54.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They expect me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to lead them to Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:26:55.275 --> 00:26:57.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( music ends, crowd applauds)</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:26:57.394 --> 00:26:58.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be okay.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:26:59.514 --> 00:27:03.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Sisko is doing everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he can to find you a place to live.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:27:04.233 --> 00:27:05.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not alone.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:27:05.512 --> 00:27:07.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope I'm not intruding.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:27:07.271 --> 00:27:08.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:27:08.910 --> 00:27:13.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, this is Varani, a great musician.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe the greatest Bajor has ever known.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:27:14.110 --> 00:27:17.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She exaggerates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but that's why I'm so fond of her.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:27:20.147 --> 00:27:21.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being a Bajoran</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:27:21.747 --> 00:27:24.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what it's like to be displaced.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:27:25.986 --> 00:27:27.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a token of friendship</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:27:28.745 --> 00:27:30.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would like to give you this.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:27:33.638 --> 00:27:36.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( playing quiet melody )</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:27:37.143 --> 00:27:42.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's from a concert I played</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>many years ago at the Jalanda Forum.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:27:57.968 --> 00:27:59.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Tumak, where have you been?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Nowhere.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:27:59.216 --> 00:28:00.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-To wash.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:28:11.812 --> 00:28:12.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer...</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:28:14.251 --> 00:28:16.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please show me a chart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this star system.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:28:25.808 --> 00:28:27.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-So, what'd your dad say?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-About what?</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:28:27.967 --> 00:28:29.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>About you getting in trouble with Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:28:29.487 --> 00:28:31.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He was very angry.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He was?</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:28:31.526 --> 00:28:33.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He always gets angry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when I get caught.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:28:35.844 --> 00:28:39.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping ) I just remembered.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have some errands to run for my uncle.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:28:40.442 --> 00:28:41.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going to have to face them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sooner or later.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:28:42.523 --> 00:28:44.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was very funny, what you did.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:28:45.442 --> 00:28:48.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, Jake?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There's a man with a sense of humor.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:28:49.921 --> 00:28:51.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nobody's laughing.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:28:51.680 --> 00:28:52.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And luckily nobody got hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:28:53.600 --> 00:28:55.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think my friend's real sorry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for what he did.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:28:58.198 --> 00:28:59.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aren't you?</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:29:00.198 --> 00:29:01.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:29:02.197 --> 00:29:03.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See? What'd I tell you?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:29:03.836 --> 00:29:05.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't sound sorry to me.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:29:10.350 --> 00:29:11.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( squealing )</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:29:20.271 --> 00:29:22.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:29:22.791 --> 00:29:27.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's enough. Break it up.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I said, break it up!</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:29:29.669 --> 00:29:30.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( snarling )</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:29:30.988 --> 00:29:31.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( growls )</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:29:32.668 --> 00:29:35.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's bad enough you're all hanging</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the station</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:29:35.307 --> 00:29:37.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>without buying anything.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have to start fighting, too?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:29:38.266 --> 00:29:40.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought we were welcome here.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:29:40.305 --> 00:29:42.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, make yourself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>welcome somewhere else.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:29:44.247 --> 00:29:45.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want us here.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:29:45.744 --> 00:29:47.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want anything to do with us.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:29:47.944 --> 00:29:50.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, we don't want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anything to do with you.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:29:51.662 --> 00:29:52.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any of you!</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:29:53.217 --> 00:29:53.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>yells </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:29:54.301 --> 00:29:55.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>hisses </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:29:57.941 --> 00:29:59.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: I can see the Skrreeans</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:29:59.500 --> 00:30:01.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>don't bother to teach</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their children manners.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:30:01.739 --> 00:30:02.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>hisses </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:30:04.418 --> 00:30:06.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Dax and I have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>combing through data on every uninhabited</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:30:06.938 --> 00:30:08.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>M-Class planet in the sector.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:08.537 --> 00:30:09.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We think that Draylon II</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:09.776 --> 00:30:11.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>would make a perfect home</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Skrreea.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:30:12.816 --> 00:30:15.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Draylon II? I've never heard of it.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:30:15.495 --> 00:30:18.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's near Sefalla Prime.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's got definite possibilities.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:30:18.734 --> 00:30:22.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stable orbit, temperate climate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a very low surface radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:30:23.253 --> 00:30:25.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Add to that good soil</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a long growing season.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:30:26.371 --> 00:30:27.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's our best bet.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:30:31.690 --> 00:30:33.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:30:39.879 --> 00:30:40.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-May we come in?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:30:50.204 --> 00:30:51.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ladies.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:30:53.844 --> 00:30:57.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive them, Commander Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They don't mean any disrespect.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:30:57.962 --> 00:30:58.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:30:59.282 --> 00:31:02.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have some encouraging news.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We think we've found a planet</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:31:02.641 --> 00:31:05.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for you and your people,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one with excellent potential</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:31:05.160 --> 00:31:06.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for resettlement.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:31:08.959 --> 00:31:14.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We appreciate all your hard work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm afraid it was unnecessary.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:31:14.397 --> 00:31:16.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, we found Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:31:17.556 --> 00:31:18.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did?</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:31:19.275 --> 00:31:21.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A planet of sorrow, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:31:22.755 --> 00:31:26.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna is your planet.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna is Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:31:36.311 --> 00:31:39.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, Stardate 47391.2.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:31:39.989 --> 00:31:41.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chief O'Brien is continuing</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to oversee repairs</i></c.bg_transparent>

493
00:31:41.989 --> 00:31:44.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Skrreean ships docked</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>at the station.</i></c.bg_transparent>

494
00:31:44.148 --> 00:31:46.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Meanwhile, Minister Rozahn</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and Vedek Sorad have arrived</i></c.bg_transparent>

495
00:31:46.748 --> 00:31:50.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>from Bajor with an official response</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Skrreeans' request to immigrate.</i></c.bg_transparent>

496
00:31:50.986 --> 00:31:53.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Major, if I may have a moment?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm sorry, Varani.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:31:53.746 --> 00:31:55.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm on my way to a meeting.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:31:55.345 --> 00:31:57.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, with Minister Rozahn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Vedek Sorad.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:31:58.642 --> 00:32:01.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I presume Haneek will be there as well.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:32:01.223 --> 00:32:04.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please tell here that my heart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>goes out to her and her people.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:32:05.183 --> 00:32:08.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell her how much Bajorans everywhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>regret having to refuse their request.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:32:09.141 --> 00:32:12.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Aren't you being a little premature?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Am I? You know what</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:32:12.100 --> 00:32:14.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the provisional government's answer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is going to be.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:32:14.259 --> 00:32:16.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>These are people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who have lost everything, Varani.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:32:16.978 --> 00:32:20.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, and I wish there was some way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we could help them.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:32:21.657 --> 00:32:25.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Bajor is in shambles, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that as well as I do.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:32:29.734 --> 00:32:31.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>First of all, I want you all to know</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:32:32.942 --> 00:32:34.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the provisional government</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has taken the Skrreeans' request</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:32:34.893 --> 00:32:37.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for immigration very seriously.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:32:38.612 --> 00:32:42.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The debate in the Chamber of Ministers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>became quite heated at times.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:32:42.811 --> 00:32:45.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Though I suppose you could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>say that about all of our debates.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:32:45.610 --> 00:32:47.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But a decision was reached?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:32:47.449 --> 00:32:50.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, I was sent here to tell you</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:32:50.768 --> 00:32:53.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the Ministers, in accord</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Vedek Assembly,</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:32:53.727 --> 00:32:56.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have decided</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to deny the Skrreeans' request.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:32:57.247 --> 00:32:58.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ROZAHN: I am sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:32:58.886 --> 00:33:02.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor simply cannot absorb</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three million refugees</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:33:02.605 --> 00:33:03.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>at this time.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:33:03.644 --> 00:33:06.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After what the Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>did to our planet</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:33:06.284 --> 00:33:07.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we can barely take care of our own.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:33:08.323 --> 00:33:10.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But no one is asking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you to take care of us.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:33:11.202 --> 00:33:12.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This decision is not based</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:33:12.801 --> 00:33:15.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>strictly on Bajoran self-interest.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:33:16.561 --> 00:33:18.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such a huge increase in population</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:33:18.560 --> 00:33:21.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>would prove to be tragic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your people as well as ours.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:33:21.400 --> 00:33:23.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Bajor has more than enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>room for us.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:33:23.559 --> 00:33:26.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The plains of the Northwest Peninsula</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are practically uninhabited.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:33:27.118 --> 00:33:28.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The land's ideal for farming.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:33:28.956 --> 00:33:30.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It used to be</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:30.717 --> 00:33:32.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>before the Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>got their hands on it.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:33.396 --> 00:33:36.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Minister Rozahn,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Skrreea are farmers.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:36.954 --> 00:33:38.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just give us the land.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:33:38.275 --> 00:33:40.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guarantee you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can make it thrive again.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:33:41.233 --> 00:33:44.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Under ideal circumstances,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>perhaps you could.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:33:44.672 --> 00:33:47.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But what if the circumstances</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aren't ideal?</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:33:47.992 --> 00:33:49.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if we go through</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another long winter?</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:50.151 --> 00:33:51.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if your crops fail?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:52.150 --> 00:33:53.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if the famine</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:33:53.389 --> 00:33:55.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that has been plaguing Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>continues to spread?</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:33:56.189 --> 00:33:57.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What then?</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:33:57.869 --> 00:33:59.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are willing to take that risk.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:33:59.827 --> 00:34:01.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ROZAHN: I'm afraid we aren't.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:34:01.267 --> 00:34:02.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ran a series of projections</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:34:02.986 --> 00:34:05.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to see whether a Skrreean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>settlement could survive</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:34:05.106 --> 00:34:06.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the Northwest peninsula.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:34:07.265 --> 00:34:09.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The results were not encouraging.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:34:10.465 --> 00:34:11.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Haneek?</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:34:11.544 --> 00:34:13.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you should seriously consider</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:13.224 --> 00:34:14.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Draylon II as an alternate to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:15.263 --> 00:34:18.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The winters are mild.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There's plenty of good farmland.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:18.102 --> 00:34:20.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! Projections can be wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:34:21.302 --> 00:34:23.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SORAD: But what if they're not?</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:34:23.381 --> 00:34:26.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is Bajor to do if your people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>start dying?</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:34:27.180 --> 00:34:30.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought I made that clear.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We are not expecting your help.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:34:30.538 --> 00:34:33.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you really think we could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>stand by and do nothing?</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:34:33.817 --> 00:34:37.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We would feel obligated to help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with food, with clothing</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:34:37.256 --> 00:34:40.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-with whatever it would take.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And where would that aid come from?</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:34:41.215 --> 00:34:43.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SORAD: Our resources are already depleted.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:34:43.655 --> 00:34:46.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To help you would mean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>depriving our own people.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:34:47.413 --> 00:34:50.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am afraid the decision</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the provisional government is final.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:34:51.812 --> 00:34:54.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreea will have to find somewhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>else to live.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:34:56.811 --> 00:34:59.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, talk to them.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:35:00.500 --> 00:35:01.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell them they're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:35:03.529 --> 00:35:04.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Help us.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:35:08.247 --> 00:35:09.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:35:11.487 --> 00:35:12.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, Haneek...</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:35:14.862 --> 00:35:15.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But they're right. I wish they weren't.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:35:16.165 --> 00:35:18.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish Bajor was Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:35:20.124 --> 00:35:21.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it's not.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:35:24.643 --> 00:35:27.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's still Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:35:37.119 --> 00:35:38.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:35:38.518 --> 00:35:39.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look at this!</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:35:45.116 --> 00:35:46.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:35:48.236 --> 00:35:50.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you like cake</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the icoberry torte is really good.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:35:51.115 --> 00:35:53.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that big-eared troll</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>really your friend?</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:35:53.274 --> 00:35:54.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He's an idiot.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:35:55.353 --> 00:35:56.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not the first to say that.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:35:57.312 --> 00:35:59.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he's not such a bad guy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>once you get to know him.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:36:00.312 --> 00:36:02.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't plan on being</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around here that long.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:36:03.151 --> 00:36:05.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My dad says you're probably</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>going to Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:36:05.430 --> 00:36:06.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Does he?</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:36:06.710 --> 00:36:08.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, sounds like a nice place.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:36:08.949 --> 00:36:10.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you want to move there?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:36:10.389 --> 00:36:11.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:36:12.285 --> 00:36:13.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither do I.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:36:19.306 --> 00:36:20.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:36:21.305 --> 00:36:22.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:36:29.583 --> 00:36:30.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek...</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:36:33.142 --> 00:36:35.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The thing I don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is why you pretended</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:36:35.581 --> 00:36:36.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:36:37.461 --> 00:36:38.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wasn't pretending.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:36:39.819 --> 00:36:40.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah!</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:36:40.819 --> 00:36:42.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you are my friend...</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:36:43.378 --> 00:36:44.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until I need you.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:36:49.377 --> 00:36:52.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know it's hard for you to see right now</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I am trying to help.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:36:53.216 --> 00:36:55.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think I've had quite enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your help.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:36:56.175 --> 00:36:57.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got to believe me.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:36:57.494 --> 00:36:59.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Sisko has found</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you a wonderful home.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:37:00.533 --> 00:37:02.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You betrayed me, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:37:02.693 --> 00:37:03.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:37:04.772 --> 00:37:06.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I honestly believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the provisional government</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:37:06.851 --> 00:37:07.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>made the right decision</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:37:08.131 --> 00:37:09.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>both for Bajor and the Skrreeans.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:37:10.570 --> 00:37:13.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If that's true,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have nothing more to discuss.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:37:17.128 --> 00:37:19.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping we could still be friends.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:37:20.208 --> 00:37:22.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So in other words, you came here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>looking for forgiveness.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:37:25.693 --> 00:37:26.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I don't forgive you.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:37:29.645 --> 00:37:30.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sisko to Kira.</i></c.bg_transparent>

609
00:37:31.485 --> 00:37:32.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:37:32.804 --> 00:37:33.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Is Haneek with you?</i></c.bg_transparent>

611
00:37:34.123 --> 00:37:34.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:37:35.385 --> 00:37:38.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I need both of you in Ops immediately.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tumak has taken a ship.</i></c.bg_transparent>

613
00:37:38.522 --> 00:37:39.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>He's headed for Bajor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

614
00:37:57.197 --> 00:37:59.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-They're not responding, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Keep trying, Mr. O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:37:59.476 --> 00:38:00.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did this happen?</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:38:00.796 --> 00:38:02.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>With all the traffic around the station</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:38:02.595 --> 00:38:04.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak and two of his friends</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were able to slip away.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:38:04.674 --> 00:38:07.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We didn't even know the ship was gone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until the Bajorans contacted us.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:38:08.741 --> 00:38:10.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, I need for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to try to talk to your son.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:38:10.872 --> 00:38:13.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a high-energy radiation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>leak in the port nacelle.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:38:13.672 --> 00:38:16.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've tried to make him aware of it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he refuses to acknowledge us.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:38:16.391 --> 00:38:18.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, open a channel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Skrreean vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:38:19.110 --> 00:38:20.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:38:22.349 --> 00:38:23.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ready.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:38:26.428 --> 00:38:27.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak?</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:38:29.227 --> 00:38:30.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Listen to me.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:38:32.226 --> 00:38:33.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your ship's in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:38:34.625 --> 00:38:37.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( quietly ) Have him turn off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>his engines and drift</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:38:37.505 --> 00:38:39.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>until the Bajorans can tractor him in.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:38:40.224 --> 00:38:43.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, turn off your engines.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:38:43.782 --> 00:38:46.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must turn your engines off, now!</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:38:48.421 --> 00:38:49.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not responding.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:38:50.220 --> 00:38:52.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, this is serious!</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:38:52.740 --> 00:38:54.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your life is in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:38:54.299 --> 00:38:56.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The others who are with you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their lives are in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:38:56.619 --> 00:38:58.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please! Answer me!</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:38:59.980 --> 00:39:00.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( console beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:39:01.174 --> 00:39:03.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sensors are detecting two Bajoran vessels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>closing in on the Skrreean ship.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:39:04.174 --> 00:39:08.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Display it here. Mr. O'Brien,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>patch us into the Bajoran interceptor.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:39:08.335 --> 00:39:09.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'BRIEN: Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:39:09.415 --> 00:39:11.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>BAJORAN: Entered restricted space.</i></c.bg_transparent>

642
00:39:11.255 --> 00:39:13.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You must turn around</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and leave immediately.</i></c.bg_transparent>

643
00:39:13.254 --> 00:39:14.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a channel.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:39:14.414 --> 00:39:16.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Major Kira</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Nerys on Deep Space 9.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:39:17.928 --> 00:39:19.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreean vessel has refused</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to acknowledge our hails.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:39:19.572 --> 00:39:21.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Communications may be down.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have to let them land.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:39:22.251 --> 00:39:24.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>That's impossible, Major.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>We have strict orders</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>not to allow</i></c.bg_transparent>

648
00:39:24.530 --> 00:39:25.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>any Skrreean vessel to land.</i></c.bg_transparent>

649
00:39:26.249 --> 00:39:27.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pilot's just a boy.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:39:27.330 --> 00:39:30.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He took the ship without permission.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's barely operational.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:39:30.289 --> 00:39:31.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: We're not even sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'll make it back here.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:39:32.484 --> 00:39:33.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm sorry, Major, but we have our orders.</i></c.bg_transparent>

653
00:39:34.877 --> 00:39:35.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who gave you those orders?</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:39:35.167 --> 00:39:36.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They come directly from General Hazar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

655
00:39:36.727 --> 00:39:38.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax, get me General Hazar on Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:39:39.464 --> 00:39:42.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell his people it's an emergency.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want to speak to him now.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:39:42.245 --> 00:39:43.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by, interceptor.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:39:43.165 --> 00:39:45.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>General Hazar will be countermanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>those orders any minute.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:39:46.244 --> 00:39:48.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The interceptor is closing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the Skrreean ship.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:39:51.482 --> 00:39:53.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's General Hazar, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:39:53.442 --> 00:39:54.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:39:54.482 --> 00:39:56.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>What is this about, Commander?</i></c.bg_transparent>

663
00:39:56.801 --> 00:39:59.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's about the Skrreean vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's approaching Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:39:59.240 --> 00:40:01.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've already given the orders</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to have it turned back.</i></c.bg_transparent>

665
00:40:01.720 --> 00:40:04.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That ship is being flown by a child</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it's leaking radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:40:05.558 --> 00:40:06.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>A child?</i></c.bg_transparent>

667
00:40:06.438 --> 00:40:07.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PILOT: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Skrreean ship. Repeating.</i></c.bg_transparent>

668
00:40:08.774 --> 00:40:11.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Return to the space station now.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Have him shut down his engines.</i></c.bg_transparent>

669
00:40:11.636 --> 00:40:13.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll tow him back.</i></c.bg_transparent>

670
00:40:13.196 --> 00:40:16.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, please, turn your engines off.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:40:17.114 --> 00:40:18.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( shots firing )</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:40:18.434 --> 00:40:19.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interceptor One, what's going on?</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:40:20.743 --> 00:40:22.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They've opened fire on us.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Taking evasive action.</i></c.bg_transparent>

674
00:40:22.353 --> 00:40:23.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, don't do this!</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:40:23.832 --> 00:40:25.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>PILOT: We've been hit!</i></c.bg_transparent>

676
00:40:25.352 --> 00:40:26.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, they're returning fire.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:40:26.912 --> 00:40:27.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:40:27.912 --> 00:40:30.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Disengage, interceptor! Repeat, disengage.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:40:30.550 --> 00:40:33.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>General, tell your pilots</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to hold their fire.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:40:34.750 --> 00:40:36.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relaying that order now.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:40:41.147 --> 00:40:42.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sobs )</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:40:44.387 --> 00:40:45.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interceptor One.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:40:46.546 --> 00:40:49.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The Skrreean ship exploded.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I didn't even think we hit it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

684
00:40:50.905 --> 00:40:53.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The phaser beam must've ignited</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the radiation leak.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:40:55.863 --> 00:40:58.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm very sorry, Commander.</i></c.bg_transparent>

686
00:40:58.702 --> 00:41:00.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all are, General.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:41:32.772 --> 00:41:35.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just stopped by to wish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you luck on Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:41:36.131 --> 00:41:39.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, I still believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this is the best choice...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:41:40.104 --> 00:41:42.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For Bajor and for you.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:41:42.649 --> 00:41:45.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You still believe we would have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a burden to your people?</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:41:47.327 --> 00:41:48.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:41:49.741 --> 00:41:51.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you've made a terrible mistake.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:41:51.766 --> 00:41:52.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of you.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:41:53.166 --> 00:41:54.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we could have helped you.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:41:55.365 --> 00:41:57.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we could have helped each other.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:41:57.804 --> 00:42:01.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreeans are farmers, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have a famine on your planet.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:42:02.683 --> 00:42:05.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps we could have made</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that peninsula bloom again.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:42:06.322 --> 00:42:07.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HANEEK: We'll never know, will we?</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:42:08.721 --> 00:42:10.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fifty years of Cardassian rule</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:42:10.721 --> 00:42:13.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have made you all frightened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and suspicious.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:42:15.479 --> 00:42:17.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel sorry for you.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:42:22.237 --> 00:42:23.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were right.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:42:24.676 --> 00:42:26.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor is not Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

